                    <p style="color: #bfdbfe; font-size: 0.9rem;">We screen thousands to hire the best. Our rigorous vetting process ensures you only get senior-level developers with proven track records.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <div class="feature-icon-box">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
